{"tid":1615102,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"除左鎖鏈結界，風箏線結界有冇得諗","createTime":"2019-10-03T03:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:19:12.000Z","uid":270905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dcf90d1dde42c481ee3449146f7b1ee47632136b","tid":1615102,"uid":270905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:43:08.000Z","msg":"之前睇新聞見話電單車手揸車既時候被風箏線纏頸<strong>割喉</strong>就知呢樣又<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">韌</span></span>又<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">透明</span></span>仲要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">利</span></span>既野有幾危險 <a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/world/ebvbogn.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fworld%2Febvbogn.html&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=60fb17d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/world/ebvbogn.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Vs0Ouad1SuU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVs0Ouad1SuU&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=d2f237ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Vs0Ouad1SuU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/society/286opr.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fsociety%2F286opr.html&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=61e47005\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/society/286opr.html</a><br />\n如果拎黎綁係馬路上面，唔洗高，就小腿中間，班popo衝過黎追人既時候會唔會唔小心自己跌親？<br />\n唔止係馬路上面，黨鐵出口入都綁多兩條，頸位又得，心口位又得，腳位又得，睇下班popo仲敢唔敢衝咁快。<br />\n衝得快，跌得快，纏得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為前線掙取撤退時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAR0ovj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAR0ovj.jpg&h=c59e99ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66993cddd78a78b7153134d4a658ca97a6d50202","tid":1615102,"uid":242438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"推"},